title: Oat Crop Acreage for England, Wales, Scotland, Great Britain
notes:
Data For 1866 Is Not Strictly Comparable With Later Data Because Of Changes In The Method Of Reporting. Source: Great Britain Agriculture And Fisheries Board, Agricultural Statistics (Prior To 1901 Called Agricultural Returns), 1866-1885 Annual Issues (Bound With Parliamentary Papers); 1894, P. 95; 1904, P. 89; 1914, P. 171; 1924, P. 85; 1932, P. 89; 1934, P. 89; 1937, P. 42. Also See The U.S. Department Of Agriculture, Agricultural Statistics, 1936, P. 46; 1939, P. 62; And The Oxford Economic Research Institute, The Agricultural Register, 1938/1939, P. 243.

This NBER data series a01037b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.
